                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "This vessel can move through sea ice up to 20 feet thick, leaving a path of open water behind it."
                },
                {
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "ability",
                    "name": "Sluggish",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "This vehicle must move twice its length for each 90-degree turn it makes."
                },
                {
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "ability",
                    "name": "Weapon Mounts",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "This vehicle has eight weapon mounts; one each on the bow and stern, and three mounted on each side. At purchase, these weapon mounts are initially empty. Installing or uninstalling a weapon into a mount requires 1 day, a successful DC 40 Crafting check, and an appropriate weapon. The weapon mounts can be equipped with Huge or smaller ranged siege weapons.",
